<HEADLINE>  Clinton Signs $15B Kosovo-Aid Bill </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	WASHINGTON (AP) -- President Clinton today signed a bill  
providing $15 billion for the air assault on Yugoslavia, aid for 
disaster victims, farm aid and other programs. But he cautioned 
Congress that veto battles over budget bills may lie ahead. 
</P>
